						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of land (?) for the maintenance of five temple drummers with 30 <hi rend="italic">kalam</hi> of paddy each (per annum) by <hi rend="bold">Ādittaṉ Vīmaṉ</hi> of Kumārapāḍi in Ma[y*]yūr-nāḍu of Kaḷattūr-kōṭṭam. This has been assigned to <hi rend="bold">Ariñjaya</hi> (<hi rend="italic">M.E.R</hi> for 1928, Part II, para 3.)</p>						

						</summary>
